snippet.title: Sonic Stranded - SAGE 2020 Demo teaser [UNCUT!]
snippet.description:
Sonic Amateur Games Expo 2020 trailer is out! This is the original video that I sent to SAGE staff. I got 3 good seconds cut from the middle, so here is a full version of that teaser.
This teaser features sneak peak at both stages in the next demo.


Music: Onlap - Miracle
